BT /F1 10 Tf 54 643 Td (GrocerEaseIMS is a PHP and MySQL inventory management system for grocery product control. It) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 629 Td (supports authenticated admin access, product records, categories, suppliers,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 615 Td (product-supplier links, stock quantities, inventory movement logs, archived records,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 601 Td (reporting charts, and database backup and recovery.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 574 Td (2. Objectives) Tj ET
0.85 w 54 554 m 558 554 l S
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538 Td (- Maintain accurate product, supplier, category, stock, and movement data.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524 Td (- Allow administrators to add, update, archive, restore, and permanently delete records.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 510 Td (- Provide dashboard visibility for active products, categories, suppliers, stock, low) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 496 Td (stock, and out-of-stock items.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 482 Td (- Protect system data through full SQL database backup and verified recovery.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 460 Td (3. Main Modules) Tj ET
0.85 w 54 440 m 558 440 l S
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 424 Td (- Authentication: validates admin login before allowing inventory access.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 410 Td (- Dashboard: displays KPIs, charts, inventory trends, and quick actions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 396 Td (- Products and Categories: manages grocery product details and classification.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 382 Td (- Suppliers and Product Suppliers: tracks supplier information and preferred supplier) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 368 Td (cost.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 354 Td (- Stock Control: records stock in and stock out transactions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 340 Td (- Archived Records: supports recovery or hard deletion of archived products, categories,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 326 Td (and suppliers.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 312 Td (- Backup and Recovery: creates full SQL backups, validates restore files, and restores) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 298 Td (the database.) Tj ET
